ld require destructive or cross-workspace actions.\n\n## Final Output Contract\nReturn a JSON object matching runtime/arckit-runtime/schemas/runtime-result.schema.json. Do not wrap it in Markdown.\n\n## Runtime Options\n- max_rounds: 1\n- adapter: codex-app-server","text_elements":[]}]},"threadId":"019f3daa-575b-7d50-85de-43c5221bdc9f","turnId":"019f3daa-5787-7f62-8f5d-5b6e928bdb35","startedAtMs":1783446001548}}}
